column1: Foster Care Youth1 Enrolled2 in NYC Public Schools During SY 2018-2019
Foster Care Youth Enrolled in High School at the End of the School Year Who are On Track to Graduate4, SY 2018-2019
1 Includes youth in 24 hour care status, on trial discharge and absent from care.
2 Enrollment data consider all students who enrolled at any point in the year between September 5, 2018 through July 1, 2019.
4  "On track" status is measured by cohort and credit accumulation for each high school grade level as of  August 31 2019
*The number of youth in cells with less than six youth are not shown to protect anonymity.
